    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        The study population is composed of 15 healthy volunteers with no history of VTE (group
        &quot;T&quot;) and 100 patients with VTE (group &quot;P&quot;). Fifteen randomly selected members of group P
        make up the sub-group &quot;Px&quot;.
      </textblock>
